name: Calantha
description: Calantha is a light blue dice with a smooth and glossy finish. Its unique design features a simple yet elegant look, with the light blue color giving it a serene and peaceful appearance.

name: Drusilla
description: When holding Drusilla, a warm and natural pulse can be felt.

name: Beleiko
description: Made from rock, said to have been formed from powerful Morph magic.

name: Vane
description: A simple red dice with a fierce amount of good luck.

name: Nylvan
description: Do not underestimate the power of a balanced tool.

name: Iyndaril
description: Some call it beginners luck but natural talent can't be taught.

name: Eleri
description: Eleri is a black woven dice usually used by the mysterious or sophisticated.

name: Seraphine
description: Seraphine is a simple yet elegant brown dice. The simplicity of its design makes it easy to read.

name: Lirien
description: I think this is actually a rock from the moon or something!

name: Meliora
description: The stones in Meliora City are rugged and earthy. The makers of this dice have done a good job turning it into a modern look.

name: Kethriel
description: Kethriel is a metallic dice that exudes power and strength. Perfect for players who prefer a more assertive and dominant gaming style.

name: Eiluned
description: Eiluned is a metallic dice with a unique triangular pattern. Its triangular design features polished, silver triangles. The geometric triangular pattern triangulates from the triangle; Triangle.

name: Dariana
description: With Dariana in hand, players will feel like they're holding a piece of modern art, imbued with the power to control fate itself.

name: Calliope
description: Calliope is a metallic dice that is sure to add a touch of edge to any game.  The chains are carefully woven together to form a solid and sturdy dice.

name: Azmarion
description: Azmarion is a mesmerizing blue dice that is said to have been forged in the deepest trenches of the ocean.

name: Sariel
description: A fragment of a powerful and ancient crystal, Sariel is a pink translucent dice that posesses an otherworldly light.

name: Sylfaen
description: Legend has it that whoever holds Sylfaen in their hand is able to control the fate of their game and can predict the outcome with great accuracy.

name: Quirien
description: Found within rituals and ceremonies. The dots on the dice are said to symbolize the stars in the sky.

name: Niamh
description: The artisans who created it believed that the blue and white color scheme symbolizes balance and harmony.

name: Melantha
description: Melantha is a yellow, durable dice with a glossy finish and well-balanced design, perfect for any game.

name: Varian
description: Varian is a dark red dice that exudes a sense of power and intensity. Its deep red color gives it a bold and striking appearance, making it stand out on any game board.

name: Kyriezi
description: A green snakeskin dice. The red is also snakeskin. Its all snakeskin. Well, the numbers are white paint.

name: Gorua
description: Gorua is a polished brown wood dice that permiates a sense of warmth and naturalness.

name: Isolde
description: Isolde is a perfect choice for players who want to add a touch of rustic charm to their game play.

name: Galadrin
description: Galadrinis an impressive dice due to its simplicity and contrast. Blood red numbers against a dark obsidian black background is sure to strike fear into your enemies.

name: Finnian
description: Finnian is the word used to describe jewellery in the upper classes of Morreth. Finnian is pure diamond encased by pure ruby. The numbers on this dice were formed by etching away the ruby to reveal the diamond beneath.

name: Brynley
description: Brynley has been in the family for over 20 generations. It still looks pretty good considering.

name: Munceymax
description: Munceymax created this dice out of iron by himself. Without trading anyone.

name: Aelorp
description: So I said Aelorp ? What do I look like to you ? Stropoda ? .. pause for laughter..

name: Kethrief
description: Kethrief displays an intricate blue and black hexagonal pattern that captures the eye instantly. While the creators of this dice were perfectionists, they made sure to leave something for the obsessive compulsive to talk about.

name: Trenkalen
description: Don't be fooled by Trenkalen's sleek appearance. Trenkalen is one of the hottest materials in its resting state. Many have tried to roll this dice, many have failed.

name: Drogathion
description: Discovered deep within a dark hole, in an unknown location, by forgotten tribes. Maybe it glows in the dark.

name: Vyrnaxis
description: A simple dice, but not for the simple minded. Vyrnaxis weaponry can only be wielded by heroes and legends, those who make history, or stop it... Vyrnaxis dice on the other hand can be wielded by anyone.

name: Kynzyron
description: Kynzyron stones have an almost metallic appearance but they are, in fact, only stone. Each Kynzyron dice takes two years to craft and are relatively rare to come by.

name: Fyryndril
description: Fyryndril represents light where there is nothing but darkness. Carriers of Fyryndril report a calming and aligning sense.

name: Kyrzulon
description: Kyrzulon is a display dice. Usually found in museums or houses owned by the wealthy. A beautiful white stone carved by hand and worn by time. Watch out for its sharp, broken corners; They are unforgiving.

name: Lyrnokar
description: An ancient dice used by nobles, commonly theived by Spearguards before entering tournaments

name: Myzmarion
description: Imbued with emerald veins and smooth to touch, roll your way to victory in style

name: Pryndaril
description: Support your team! GO Pryndarils!

name: Tyvralen
description: When spinning this dice on its point, the grey and blue mix together to form a spectacular livid.

name: Uryzynar
description: Uryzynar is a dice for the hardened. One who has seen many victories, and many defeats.

name: Vyndarion
description: This immensely strong dice was smithed by melting down the sword of Vyndarion; A sword oringally forged for giants.

name: Wyzmaril
description: 'I respect wood, I revere wood.'
